      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle and heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coriander seeds</strong> and<strong> fennel seeds</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant and toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so they don't burn!</p><p>Once toasted, transfer to a <strong>food processor</strong> and reserve the pan for later</p>",
