    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the<strong> basa fillets</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper </strong>and chop them into rough bite-sized pieces</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>basa</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until golden</p><p>Once browned, add the <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and cook for a further 1 min</p><p>Transfer the<strong> cooked basa</strong> to a plate, reserve the pan</p>",
